      "passage_index": 18,
      "title": "Phonology",
      "score": 0.05679958923634225,
      "text": "Phonology\nBroadly speaking, government phonology (or its descendant, strict-CV phonology) has a greater following in the United Kingdom, whereas optimality theory is predominant in the United States.[citation needed]",
