      "score": 0.07008244617800838,
      "text": "The Woman with You\n\"The Woman with You\" is a song written by David Frasier and Craig Wiseman and recorded by American country music artist Kenny Chesney. It was released in August 2004 as the fourth single from Chesney’s 2004 album \"When the Sun Goes Down\". The song peaked at number 2 on the U.S. \"Billboard\" Hot Country Singles & Tracks chart in 2004.",
